casebody.data:
Candy STREZINSKI, Employee
v.
CITY OF GREENSBORO, Employer and
Key Risk Management Services, Carrier. No. 23P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 9, 2008. Kathleen G. Sumner, Greensboro, for Candy Strezinski. Caroline Lock, Greensboro, for City of Greensboro, et al. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 654 S.E.2d 263 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th day of January 2008 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th day of October 2008."
